title: Bullish Two Hundred Day Moving Average Cross - H - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of Hyatt Hotels Corp (Symbol: H) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $73.13, changing hands as high as $74.37 per share. Hyatt Hotels Corp shares are currently trading up about 2.2% on the day.
